This is a very base project included:
- Spring MVC 3.2.2
- HTML 5 Boilerplate
- Bootstrap

To be added:
- Hibernate
- Spring security

Prerequisite:
 - gradle installed
 - JDK


Usage:
- Windows
	1. go to project root directory
	2. run setenv.cmd
	3. run "gradle idea" or "gradle eclipse"
	4. run "gradle jettyRunWar"
	5. open the project in your IntelliJ/Eclipse


Folder structure:

-liruda
   -src
        -main
            -java
            -webapp